10:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-600 leading-relaxed","children":"uBlock Origin is a popular open-source content blocker for browsers. It blocks ads, trackers, and malware domains using community-maintained filter lists. It's widely regarded as the most efficient ad blocker available, with low CPU and memory footprint. However, it only focuses on content blocking — it doesn't include any productivity, wellness, or screen capture tools."}]
